;HETEROGEN
THE POSITIONS OF THE ATOMS OF THE NITROXIDE 
RING OF R7A ARE NOT UNIQUE, AS THOSE PARTICULAR 
ATOMS WERE NOT RESOLVED IN EITHER CONFORMATION 
(A OR B).  COORDINATES FOR ATOMS OF THE NITROXIDE 
RING WERE DEPOSITED IN A MINIMUM ENERGY CONFIGURATION.
